RIL MO-MENEENA WA LE-FAATEMA-TE WAL HASANE WAL HUSAINE.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَی الْاَئِمَۃِ مِنْ ذُرِیَّۃِ الْحُسَیْنِ عَلَیْهِمُ السَّلَامُ وَرَحَمَۃُ اللهِ وَبَرَكَاتُهٗ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ اَیُّهَا الْعَبْدُ الصَّالِحُ یَا مَیْثَمُ بْنَ یَحْیَی التَّمَارِ الْمُطِیْعُ لِلهِ وَلِرَسُوْلِهٖ وَلْاَمِیْرِ الْمُؤْمِنِیْنَ وَلِفَاطِمَۃِ وَالْحَسَنِ وَالْحُسَیْنِ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013628, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "I testify that you established the prayer, paid zakat, enjoined the good, forbade the evil, and strove for the sake of Allah as is due to Him. You worked according to His book, following the righteous and pursuing the Prophets.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "ASH-HADO ANNA-KA QAD AQAM-TAS SALAATA WA ATAI-TAZ ZAKAATA WA AMAR-TA BIL MA’ROOFE WA NA-HAITA A’NIL MUNKARE WA JAA-HADTA FIL LAAHE HAQQA JAHAADE-HI WA A’MILTA BE-KETAABE-HI MUQTADE-YAN BIS SAALE-HEENA WA MUTTABE-A’N LIN NABIY-YEENA.", "ArabicText1": "اَشْهَدُ اَنَّكَ قَدْ اَقَمْتَ الصَّلَوۃَ وَاَتَیْتَ الزَّكَاۃَ وَاَمَرْتَ بِالْمَعْرُوْفِ وَنَهَیْتَ عَنِ الْمُنْكَرِ وَجَاهَدْتَ فِیْ اللهِ حَقَّ جَهَادِهٖ وَعَمِلْتَ بِكِتَابِهٖ مُقْتَدِیًا بِالصَّالِحِیْنَ وَمُتَّبِعًا لِلنَّبِیِّیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013629, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "I testify that you were slain unjustly. May Allah curse those who oppressed and accused you and ordered your murder. May Allah curse those who prepared the grounds for animosity and hatred against you, till the Day of Judgement. May Allah fill their graves with fire and prepare for them a painful chastisement.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "WA ASH-HADO ANNA-LA QOTIL-TA MAZLOO-MAN FA-LA-A’NAL LAAHO MAN ZALAMA-KA WA MAN IF-TARAA A’LAIKA WA MAN AMARA BE-QATLA-KA WA LA-A’NAL LAAHO MAN NASABA LAKAL A’DAA-WATA WAL BA-GHA-ZAA-A ILAA YAWMIL QAYAAMATE WAHSHAL LAAHO QABOORA-HUM NAARAN WA A-A’DDA LAHUM A’ZAA-BAN ALEE-MAN.", "ArabicText1": "وَاَشْهَدُ اَنَّكَ قُتِلْتَ مَظْلُوْمًا فَلَعَنَ اللهُ مَنْ ظَلَمَكَ وَمَنْ اِفْتَرٰی عَلَیْكَ وَمَنْ اَمَرَ بِقَتْلَكَ وَلَعَنَ اللهُ مَنْ نَصَبَ لَكَ الْعَدَاوَۃَ وَالْبَغَضَائَ اِلٰی یَوْمِ الْقِیَامَۃِ وَحْشَی اللهُ قُبُوْرَهُمْ نَارًا وَاَعَدَّ لَهُمْ عَذَابًا اَلِیْمًا۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedS